WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.800
With Posit Workbench, you have the flexibility to build any Python data product in your preferred

00:00:09.800 --> 00:00:13.120
IDE.

00:00:13.120 --> 00:00:23.040
Create web applications, such as Streamlit, Bokeh, Dash, or Shiny, to best suit your needs.

00:00:23.040 --> 00:00:25.200
Collaborate and scale with ease.

00:00:25.200 --> 00:00:29.920
And then simply deploy in Posit Connect to get your data science projects in the hands

00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:33.599
of stakeholders quickly and securely.

00:00:33.599 --> 00:00:35.919
If you can dream it, you can build it.

